commit.message:
Adding cmake project

Updated documentation, added version autogeneration based on version of project.

Miscellaneous fixes

Updated usage info, removed unused and undefined pieces of code.
Update copyrights for all project's files

Updated project infrastructure info

Added README.md and LICENSE.txt, updated info about project.

Make project more POSIX.1-2008 compliant

Removed deprecated and GNU specific extensions.
Fix inline function usage with GCC>5

Symlink support

Bug: https://bugs.gentoo.org/815823
Signed-off-by: Zac Medico <zmedico@gentoo.org>
